headline: United Airlines Gears Up to Welcome Winter With Additional Flights
summary: UAL expands its winter schedule with new routes and added flights to 15 cities, boosting service to Orlando, Fort Lauderdale, and Las Vegas.

headline: Spirit Airlines Is Struggling, and Rivals Smell Blood
summary: United Airlines and Frontier are planning new routes regularly flown by Spirit, which last week filed its second bankruptcy in less than a year.
